Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,====AVANT=====
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的婚事已經談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在了的話  就沒人陪我玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想和公人大人分開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和白亞小姐  可憐小姐  愛佳小姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就交給庶民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====APART=====
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裏就沒有什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  為什麼要拜託我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為有棲川家的人  我不能破壞這次相親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子的一切就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是外面的城市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和庶民樂園一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多警衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我的行動已經暴露給母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都拿著木刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為庶民的你先去打頭陣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁你吸引周圍的警衛的時候  我迅速潛入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想衝進那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙是用劍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來都是行家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想幹架  好像干一架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想和其他劍士比試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來看一下自己實力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不突破這裏的話就沒辦法到達有棲川那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就唯有一戰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃神領可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為劍士向你們宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐式劍技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  那幫傢伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庶民果然非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  就算是我今天也有所變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了  我的新技能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐式劍技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪裏來的特技英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想點辦法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這麼多人該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏交給我  你們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐式劍技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋風之五十八
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繚亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下  正臣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開  武宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正臣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道您不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是您差不多該離開妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正臣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正臣大人的覺悟  我清楚地感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏交給我  你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上樓梯右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝  白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  公人  你慢一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪還有那個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人之後是機器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就該我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼砸這麼準
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扔垃圾進桶可是百發百中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制室在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好  白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮  白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人  發什麼呆啊  快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞  是走這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就在這個房間的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕緊逃的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐  你這身打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座府邸中有一個與外界時間流動不一樣的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了  神樂阪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼果斷  繚亂  呵成之後  我自創出的可憐式劍技最終奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}Rising  Impact  Infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無盡上斬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}名字有點統一性好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我  你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂阪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這是什麼傷害形式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正臣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能總當個少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵入進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這位是麗子的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是擔心麗子才特地來這裏看她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在稍微有些事情  稍後再陪您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場婚事  我堅決反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本人不情願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子她並沒有不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子作為有棲川家的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常清楚這場婚事到底有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這並不是她本人的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是遵從家裏的規矩而已不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了家族而犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對我們來說也是當然而且非常重要的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子非常理解這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括這些  全都是麗子的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的事情你一介庶民又怎能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來到清華院一個多月了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可到現在還不明白大小姐這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活的世界也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的東西也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把庶民的事解釋給他們聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也傳到不到她們的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看事物的方式也全然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許之後也不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是和庶民部的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在庶民部度過的時光是那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和她告別是多麼令人傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這樣的麗子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  麗子已經決定接受這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她才沒有接受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛佳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕被人討厭  害怕被人厭煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以為這些才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這其實不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於明白了  做自己想做的事有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有公人  白亞  可憐  麗子在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我們沒資格說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  至少等到麗子能接受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她對我們而言是很重要的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人們打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人你想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子  你知道自己在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開有棲川家的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就失去了回到清華院的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清華院是只有大小姐才能就讀的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是有棲川家族的普通女生是就讀不了清華院的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你要是離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說回清華院了  你只會流浪於街頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在庶民家的話  上層的規矩就管不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然去不了清華院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法讓你獲得和以前一樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你是指
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力說服父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子我會讓你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子不才  一生請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親  母親  一直以來承蒙指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的犬子他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到麗子如此強烈的意願有些吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似受到了打擊  回大學裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳子小姐  這件事就當沒發生過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是服了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子  你就和自己的意中人結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親大人  謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂阪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子這一生就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親大人  我會幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要結婚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛不是向她求婚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然去不了清華院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法讓你獲得和以前一樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力說服父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子我會讓你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確聽上去是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於你們還小  就先訂婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去問候一下公人大人的父母才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  神樂阪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…  其實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是說完那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來告訴我並不是那個意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是庶民誒  沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  神樂阪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在變得超級討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定想讓你成為我的女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  好奇怪啊  您不是討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  超級討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要把你帶回家裏  盡情調教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教  有棲川公人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是入贅女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我堅決反對公人和麗子結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  神樂阪先生看上去也有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事已經決定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然躲過了剛剛那一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點死人了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不會把麗子交給你這種變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子永遠都是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢  當然是你妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子  阻止一下你哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100種理想的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庶民還有這麼棒的雜誌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什麼這種雜誌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了有棲川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是不想分開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組隊還是偶爾會和你一起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說想和你組隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被妹控弄死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正臣大人  請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉  說了那種不清不楚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人大人  請抬起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我過早判斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母女一起  實在是太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這件事  我這種人做有棲川小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請喊我麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗子  的丈夫  也太不要臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你們兩人在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來參加活動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法  今天我也奉陪到底  做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  公人大人  如果我真的離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人大人會收留我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要離家出走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你事到如今說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和愛佳大人沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然有關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你惹出了那麼大的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要永遠作為庶民部的基層人員呆在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的話都沒有人能主持大局了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}哈利路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}夠了  白亞  穿上內褲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:56.56,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(640,495)\fs30\fad(0,930)}不  要  消  失  在  暮  光  中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:56.56,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(640,540)\fs30\fad(0,930)}花  江  惠  理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公人那傢伙  到底在哪裏幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒說這是件壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呢  小美由紀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先把他的舌頭拔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小美由紀  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清華院也是學校  這種事也發生過好幾回
